Cyberpunk style: A glowing orange cube floats at the center of a dark, neon-lit server room, casting warm amber light across rows of sleek black monolithic servers. Holographic data streams and circuit patterns spiral around the cube like digital ribbons. The atmosphere is moody with deep purple and blue shadows contrasting against the cube's intense orange glow. Reflective floor tiles mirror the scene below. Thin fiber optic cables extend from the cube in all directions like a nervous system, pulsing with faint orange light. The composition emphasizes the cube as a central power source, mysterious and vital, surrounded by the cold technological infrastructure it commands.
